rc=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌到你條女腳都軟住灘左係張床到<br />\n班男人就一個一個咁輪鳩佢，好似屌飛機杯咁屌。<br />\n上一手男人既精液就當係潤滑劑，下一個男人就張d流緊出黎既精液隊番入走，成個閪好似刷牙咁起哂白泡。再由叻一個男人將新既精液注入去。成個陰道都裝滿其他男人既種子， 迫埋入子宮。<br />\n有咁既女，諗起都興奮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/12.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoj